name: Stilton Musk [OLD]
description: "STILTON MUSK ($STILTON) is a community token that is born out of a shared appreciation for the cheese, Stilton. Not only that, it is the preferred cheese of a certain, very rich and famous CEO. The token was unleashed in peak ''cheese season'' and became instantly legendary - gaining hundreds of holders in a few hours. The contract is unique and deflationary as it ''melts'' $STILTON with every transaction. The team will introduce NFTs and utility in order to cement its Blue-Cheese-Chip status in memecoin history. "
